query:
SELECT tr.*, ti.testType as invitationType, ti.status as invitationStatus
FROM testResults tr 
LEFT JOIN testInvitations ti ON tr.invitationId = ti.id 
WHERE tr.employeeId = 690008 
ORDER BY tr.completedAt DESC 
LIMIT 5
